                offices or used as convinience refrigerators in homes. In
                compoarison to standard fridges they are less prone to
                breakdowns. Nevertheless, they can still face problems like
                thermostat issues and condenser coil malfunctions. These fridges
                are often moved around frequently which causes them to wear and
                tear often. Make sure to regularly check the thermostat settings
                and clean the coils. It will help your mini fridge work longer.
              </p>
            </div>

